name: Pear
description: Sweet like a pear with her legs in the air. I can't help but stare. She said "What are you doing over there? Come here and taste the fruit I bare". Being the gentleman that I am, I do not deny a woman her pleasures. Like a soldier, I marched head first into battle! There were many twists and turns and we all had fun and learned something about ourselves. And that's what life should be about.
